Usage: define_bundled_bus [-help] [-add_members <string>]
                          [-delete_members <string>] [-name <string>]

-help                     # Prints out the command usage
-add_members <string>     # name of nets to be added to the group
                          # (list, optional)
-delete_members <string>  # name of nets to be deleted from the group
                          # (list, optional)
-name <string>            # name of the group (string, optional)